The '''brown-rumped bunting''' ('''''Emberiza affinis''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Emberizidae]] native to the [[Sudan (region)]] and adjacent areas. Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s.

